SVC      CSECT
R1       EQU   1
R14      EQU   14
         USING SVC,15
*
*  CHECK FOR PGM NAME TO BE PLACED HERE
*
         LTR   R1,R1         CHECK IF TO TURN ON AUTH
         BZ    AUTH          YES SO AUTHORISE-SUP MODE,KEY 0
         MODESET KEY=NZERO,MODE=PROB
*
* NOW SHOULD BE IN PROGRAM MODE AND NOT KEY 0
*
         BR    R14           RETURN
AUTH     EQU   *
         MODESET KEY=ZERO,MODE=SUP
*
* NOW SHOULD BE IN SUPVR MODE AND KEY 0
*
         BR    R14           RETURN
*
         END
